  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cesarean Myomectomy, safety and effect on uterine cavity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      this study aims to compare between women who underwent Cesarean Myomectomy and those who
      underwent Cesarean section only regarding the procedure safety and whether uterine cavity was
      affected later on.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
